para.para.body:
Notice that a hyperspace has many normal vectors: if 
                     \Vect{n}
                   is a normal  vector, so are 
                     2\cdot \Vect{n}
                  , 
                     3\cdot \Vect{n}
                  , 
                     (-1)\cdot \Vect{n}
                   and, in general, 
                     t\cdot \Vect{n}
                   for any 
                     t\neq 0
                  .
